                  "Polymyxin B was licensed in the late 1950s. The US package insert recommends a maximum daily dose of 25,000 IU/kg (2.5 mg/kg) with adjustment downward for renal insufficiency. Based on 2013 published data, the recommended dosage is generally higher and there is no need to adjust for renal insufficiency (Clin Infect Dis 2013;57:524).",
